title: IBM: PATH vs. IBM: Which AI-Related Stock Is a Better Buy Right Now?
description: In this piece, I evaluated two AI-related stocks, International Business Machines Corporation ( IBM ) and UiPath Inc. ( PATH ) , to determine which is better for an investor. I believe IBM is the better buy for the reasons explained throughout this article.
